{"tid":1877304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩火車站現可疑盒 遺「港警濫暴」","createTime":"2020-02-13T02:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T09:09:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f3df71be9d730a410a87206765a020790da65f44","tid":1877304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/WRPMD3A6U2T73CAU2EXP66NM54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FWRPMD3A6U2T73CAU2EXP66NM54%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=a1981ca1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FWRPMD3A6U2T73CAU2EXP66NM54%2F&h=86b2ad3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/WRPMD3A6U2T73CAU2EXP66NM54/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩火車站現可疑盒 遺「港警濫暴」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵大埔墟站路軌及沙田圍站對開行人路，昨凌晨兩個半小時內發現可疑紙盒，警方爆炸品處理課（EOD）人員到場引爆，證實盒內並無炸彈，兩宗案件均無人受傷，同列炸彈嚇詐，分別交由大埔警區及沙田警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200213/large/1581524540_c42f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200213%2Flarge%2F1581524540_c42f.gif&h=ff127646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【沙田圍站】拆彈機械人引爆紙盒後，盒內電池及火牛等四散。黃江奇攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEOD引爆證非炸彈<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨4時08分，港鐵巡查路軌的職員，發現大埔墟站北行近漢家路一段路軌上有一個可疑紙盒，懷疑為爆炸品，立即通知車務控制中心並報警。爆炸品處理課人員奉召到場檢視後，清晨約6時將紙盒引爆，發現內無炸彈，將盒內物品撿走調查。其間，東鐵綫服務略受影響，大埔墟站至太和站一度暫停服務，直至清晨6時許始回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200213/large/1581524540_eeb1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200213%2Flarge%2F1581524540_eeb1.gif&h=6cc0eada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【大埔墟站】港鐵職員昨凌晨巡查路軌時發現一個可疑紙盒。<br />\n<br />\n昨清晨6時22分，港鐵馬鞍山綫沙田圍站職員發現A出口對開沙角街行人路，有一個電線外露的可疑紙盒，於是報警，警方接報封閉現場調查。爆炸品處理課人員到場檢查可疑紙盒後，遙控拆彈機械人向可疑紙盒連開兩槍打穿紙盒，盒內物件四散，包括電池、線圈及火牛等，旁邊有一張濕透的A4白紙，紙上寫上「港警濫暴」等字。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃江奇"},{"pid":"a527a69f7344282c82933df70380c4ff4220e45f","tid":1877304,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:45:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">港警濫暴</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c011a7426bd5a69f215c7cba78f79e3a50a4361","tid":1877304,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37acc0378161ad7299c2763fef4e8543f7588bcd","tid":1877304,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"boxing day"},{"pid":"016d8e1cb02e9cdd085498408e74cf3f9b0f096f","tid":1877304,"uid":259749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0171a5f7deeb9d0e968ce22a3c69bb17cf0465b","tid":1877304,"uid":61653,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"正常人都寫黑警啦<br />\n寫港警係邊個所為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如大埔既民族黨放石頭一樣<br />\n邊個做呢啲野會自爆仲要咁出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869e169690f5bb83855e17d83f84f4e73d8553c1","tid":1877304,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"不錯"},{"pid":"a6f700dcf6db86240e8caa7ad4fc3b30bb9180d0","tid":1877304,"uid":159916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"connect 中國手足<img src=\"/assets/f